225
00:16:40,720 --> 00:16:42,320
[SPEAKER_02] Nemojte koristiti izraze s visokom vrijednošću.

226
00:16:42,399 --> 00:16:44,000
[SPEAKER_02] Nemojte misliti: To je nevjerojatno.

227
00:16:44,159 --> 00:16:45,600
[SPEAKER_02] To je evolucijsko.

228
00:16:46,159 --> 00:16:47,519
